node.text:
Ethan is our Acorn of the Week! After days of planning, Ethan finally made a college course schedule that he’s satisfied with. He has been actively planning for his freshman year at UC San Diego, having registered for courses, networked with current and incoming students, and found some student organizations that he wants to get involved with. He made a college bucket list to ensure his freshman year of college is well-spent doing the things he loves. 

Give him a 👏👏👏 in the comments and tell us what's on your freshman year bucket list.

Nominated by @stxnleyli

node.text: Get prepared for test day by taking a full-length practice exam on @khanacademy , and check out these other helpful study tips.
